text.section:
The subtraction under subsection (a) of this section includes the amounts allowed to be subtracted for an individual under:
§ 10-208(d) of this title (Conservation tillage equipment expenses);
§ 10-208(i) of this title (Reforestation or timber stand expenses);
§ 10-208(k) of this title (Wage expenses for targeted jobs);
§ 10-208(m) of this title (Poultry or livestock manure spreading equipment); and
§ 10-208(p) of this title (Elevator handrails in health care facilities).
